SYNOPSIS
========
   int get_eval_cost()

DESCRIPTION
===========
   Returns the remaining evaluation cost the current execution (the current 
   command) may use up.

   It starts at a driver given high value and is reduced with each executed 
   statement.

HISTORY
=======
   - changed (3.2.6) -- the initial value was made available as macro.

SEE ALSO
========
   rusage(E), command(E), query_limits(E)
